<div class="row">
    <h2>
        <strong>Worklist is High Fidelity's exoskeleton</strong>
        for rapid software development.
    </h2>
    <p>
        High Fidelity is an open source virtual world platform. We are
        building the software with a mix of full-time developers, part
        time developers who are paid here on the worklist, and open
